[I] A replacement library for the Athena (libXaw) widget set

[T] neXtaw is a replacement library for the Athena (libXaw) widget set.
[T] It is based on Xaw3d, by Kaleb Keithley and is almost 100% backward
[T] compatible with it. Its goal is to try to emulate the look and feel of the
[T] N*XTSTEP GUI.

[U] https://siag.nu/neXtaw/

